                     <title xml:lang="he">אשכול הכופר</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The volume contains an exposition of the commandments arranged under the parts of the decalogue. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 40v-42r contain a preface of the scribe. </p>
                     
                     
                     
